title: GORGEOUS FURNISHED WATER VIEW IN GRAN PARAISO!
posting_body: ['Living in this gorgeous furnished unit at Gran Paraiso is a pleasant experience.', 'The breathtaking views of the water will make you fall in love.', 'Just bring your belongings & start to enjoy a new way to live.', 'The unit is in impeccable condition & features private elevator access, kitchen appliances by Sub-Zero, a large terrace & high ceilings.', 'Large master bedroom, custom built-in walk-in closet.', '5-star amenities such as a dramatic circular zero-entry heated swimming pool overlooking the Bay, a 10,000 sf state-of-the-art fitness center, tennis courts, movie theater, business center, children’s playground, indoors/outdoors spa, teen’s game room, golf simulator, wine cellar & bowling, theater, valet parking, full-service concierge and much more.', 'Close to Wynwood, Midtown & the Design District', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
